  "interpretation": [
    "OSC-6 reported Spearman(ell_c, rank)=-0.026 on ~200 twist-pair forms. Full population (17,314 forms, all ranks): Spearman=-0.0999. After ablating rank-0 (9,400 rank>=1 classes): Spearman=-0.1708, p=1.84e-62. The NEGATIVE correlation strengthens after rank-0 ablation: higher-rank classes isolate at LOWER primes (smaller ell_c). Rank-2 mean ell_c=3.14 vs rank-1 mean ell_c=3.99. Effect is weak but highly significant.",
